Arithmetic Operations 
expr 2 + 3
expr 2 - 3
expr 2 * 3
expr 12 / 2
expr 20 % 3	

echo "The addition of 2 and 3 is:" `expr 2 + 3`
echo "The substraction of 2 over 3 is:" `expr 2 - 3`
echo "The Multiplecation of 2 and 3 is:" `expr 2 \* 3`
echo "The division 12 over 2 is:" `expr 12 / 2`
echo "The modular of 20 over 3 is:" `expr 20 % 3`  
